  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba3\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A man's body was recovered from Nawakota Public Market in Batticaloa",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kathankudi police said that an unidentified man's body was found dead in the Navakuta Public Market area of \u200b\u200bKathankudi Police Division, Batticaloa on Monday (18) morning.",
        "On the day of the incident, people who had come to the market building for business saw a dead body and informed the police.",
        "After this, the police went to the spot and in the investigation, the said person is about 60 years old, and he has not yet been identified and they are taking steps to get court permission to hand over the dead body to the hospital for post-mortem, the police said."
      ],
